      {
        "title": "What is Fever?",
        "content": "Fever is a temporary increase in body temperature, often due to illness."
      },
      {
        "title": "Causes of Fever",
        "content": "- Infections (bacterial, viral)\n- Inflammatory conditions\n- Heat exhaustion\n- Certain medications"
      },
      {
        "title": "Effects of Fever",
        "content": "- Increased metabolic rate\n- Activation of immune response\n- Discomfort and fatigue\n- Possible dehydration"
      }
    ]
  }
}
